from the evil mouse king?

1666
01:17:41,858 --> 01:17:42,891
Yeah, I know the story.

1667
01:17:42,926 --> 01:17:49,131
And all you have to do
is find him and let him out.

1668
01:17:49,165 --> 01:17:51,267
You make it sound so easy.

1669
01:17:51,300 --> 01:17:52,201
It is.

1670
01:17:52,235 --> 01:17:54,871
Eh, see how rough it is?

1671
01:17:54,903 --> 01:17:59,275
