always going with the grain.

1672
01:17:59,308 --> 01:18:04,012
And once you've made it
completely smooth...

1673
01:18:04,680 --> 01:18:06,883
You decide on a face.

1674
01:18:06,916 --> 01:18:09,252
How do you decide?

1675
01:18:09,753 --> 01:18:10,853
You just know.

1676
01:18:10,887 --> 01:18:16,059
It's a face you wanna look at
for the rest of your life.

1677
01:18:17,093 --> 01:18:20,196
That would be a nice face.

1678
01:18:20,462 --> 01:18:24,000
A very nice face.

1679
01:18:33,276 --> 01:18:35,911
Peter! Are you in there?!

1680
01:18:35,945 --> 01:18:37,781
Ah, there you are.

1681
01:18:37,814 --> 01:18:38,347
Hi, holly.

1682
01:18:38,381 --> 01:18:39,315
Peter, I'm so sorry.

1683
01:18:39,348 --> 01:18:42,251
I just stepped out for a minute.
I didn't know.

1684
01:18:42,285 --> 01:18:44,019
Know what? Wh-what's wrong?

1685
01:18:44,052 --> 01:18:45,453
Well, there was
a customer in the bar,

1686
01:18:45,488 --> 01:18:47,455
And he just fell in love
with your nutcracker,

1687
01:18:47,490 --> 01:18:48,957
And he told Chuck
he totally had to have it,

1688
01:18:48,992 --> 01:18:53,528
So Chuck named a price
that he thought was gonna be
way too crazy for anybody,

1689
01:18:53,561 --> 01:18:56,399
And the guy just bought it.

1690
01:18:58,267 --> 01:18:59,534
Sorry.

1691
01:18:59,567 --> 01:19:01,270
