1696
01:19:15,417 --> 01:19:18,353
This guy actually paid
all that money

1697
01:19:18,386 --> 01:19:20,355
For one of these little toys?

1698
01:19:20,388 --> 01:19:21,557
They're not toys, Earl.

1699
01:19:21,589 --> 01:19:24,928
They're handcrafted works of art
made by a master craftsman.

1700
01:19:24,960 --> 01:19:27,430
We're still
talkin' about Peter, right?

1701
01:19:27,462 --> 01:19:28,396
No offense.

1702
01:19:28,431 --> 01:19:29,397
None taken.

1703
01:19:29,432 --> 01:19:32,034
It's his craftsmanship
that makes them unique.

1704
01:19:32,068 --> 01:19:33,436
Each one is different.

1705
01:19:33,468 --> 01:19:34,070
$500 different.

1706
